{"tid":1389070,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我地都要玩good cap bad cap","createTime":"2019-07-30T21:20:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T21:22:33.000Z","uid":28264,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bb857233b1e600b1862d423638a4088011a79afb","tid":1389070,"uid":28264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T21:20:26.000Z","msg":"唔係要幫佢地洗白<br />\n我地玩good cap bad cap就係分化佢地<br />\n一邊係咁狂屌bad cap 一邊讚good cap<br />\n自自然佢地就會對立<br />\n<br />\n今日發夢睇立埸直播好似係果2個細佬係比人放左<br />\n但大家都唔走 忽然中指狗走出黎 話佢地走左啦 大家散啦<br />\n就係咁比人狂屌 屌撚到佢入番去<br />\n之後鄉黑就黎料 完左之後佢地係出過黎5秒 之後就入番去 (同新聞講既唔同<br />\n係因為撞左車佢地先出黎 一路上中指狗都係咁比人屌 屌到CID黎佢入番去之前都比人屌<br />\n有個朋友仲話 呢D掌聲得天水圍先有 元朗沒架<br />\n好明顯佢地玩good cap bad cap 我地都係 <br />\n拍下掌又唔洗成本 呃下你班傻仔架<br />\n事後大家都話 佢地應份架 有人工架 明顯大家心入邊係沒對佢地改觀<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我地係到死都唔會忘記班撚樣點樣對班我地</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n利申:全程睇9合1直播架渣"},{"pid":"132b4afa9d4384686a01dea530bacb19107164e1","tid":1389070,"uid":28264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T21:21:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c616279ee4630940efff02c02ea6f849baabdd74","tid":1389070,"uid":118128,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T21:21:42.000Z","msg":"Cop*"},{"pid":"d71184ae8e6fd81a6c4ea36f769741bd510baba7","tid":1389070,"uid":28264,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c616279ee4630940efff02c02ea6f849baabdd74","tid":1389070,"uid":118128,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T21:21:42.000Z","msg":"Cop*"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T21:22:33.000Z","msg":"SOR 文化水平低"}]}